data.description: OPEN HOUSE CANCELLED - Seller selecting an offer from many. Welcome to your private waterfront oasis on Pascoag Reservoir! Three levels of finished space - 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths, hardwood floors, pellet stove and so much more! Updated kitchen with granite, radiant heat under tile floor, stainless steel appliances (including double convection ovens), refrigerator and induction cooktop with microwave above. Open floor plan on the lake side provides flexible space for dining, entertaining or just relaxing with magnificent views of the lake. The rear wall of windows and slider provide 180° panoramas and the slider leads to an expansive composite deck. Two lake-view bedrooms upstairs with built in drawers, closets and eave storage. The finished basement is bright, light and modern. It completes this dream home with a guest bedroom, office or family room, full modern bath with oversized shower, summer kitchen with wine fridge and laundry area. Walk out basement exits to a private paver patio and continue towards the lake over the lush green backyard. Picture your lakefront fires in the firepit on the second patio by the water. Drop your boat in the water and tie it to the aluminum dock. Shed & under-deck storage. And did I mention it is Meticulously Maintained??!
